<view class="feedback-container page-container data-v-29f06c90"><view class="feedback-tips card rounded-lg shadow-base data-v-29f06c90"><text class="tip-icon data-v-29f06c90">💡</text><text class="data-v-29f06c90">我们非常重视您的每一个建议和遇到的问题，请详细描述，我们会尽快处理！</text></view><form data-event-opts="{{[['submit',[['submitFeedback',['$event']]]]]}}" bindsubmit="__e" class="data-v-29f06c90"><view class="form-section card rounded-lg shadow-base data-v-29f06c90"><view class="form-item data-v-29f06c90"><text class="item-label data-v-29f06c90">反馈内容 <text class="required-star data-v-29f06c90">*</text></text><textarea class="textarea-field rounded-base data-v-29f06c90" name="content" placeholder="请详细描述您遇到的问题或建议..." maxlength="1000" auto-height="{{true}}" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','content','$event',[]],['formData']]]]]}}" value="{{formData.content}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea><view class="char-counter data-v-29f06c90">{{$root.g0+"/1000"}}</view></view><view class="form-item data-v-29f06c90"><text class="item-label data-v-29f06c90">相关截图 (可选，最多3张)</text><view class="image-uploader data-v-29f06c90"><view class="image-preview-list data-v-29f06c90"><block wx:for="{{formData.images}}" wx:for-item="image" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><view class="image-preview-item data-v-29f06c90"><image src="{{image}}" mode="aspectFill" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['previewImage',[index]]]]]}}" bindtap="__e" class="data-v-29f06c90"></image><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['removeImage',[index]]]]]}}" class="remove-image-btn data-v-29f06c90" bindtap="__e"><text class="uni-icon uni-icon-closeempty data-v-29f06c90"></text></view></view></block><block wx:if="{{$root.g1<3}}"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['chooseImages',['$event']]]]]}}" class="add-image-btn data-v-29f06c90" bindtap="__e"><text class="uni-icon uni-icon-plusempty data-v-29f06c90"></text></view></block></view></view></view><view class="form-item data-v-29f06c90"><text class="item-label data-v-29f06c90">联系方式 (选填)</